Grounded Container Ship Leaking Oil off Norway, VG Reports

-- B y   J o n a s   B e r g m a n
-- 
2011-02-18T08:32:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-18/grounded-container-ship-leaking-oil-off-norway-vg-reports.html
The Godafoss container ship is
leaking oil after grounding off Ytre Hvaler national park in
southern  Norway , VG reported, citing local Mayor Eivind Norman
Borge.   The ship may hold as much as 500 tons of crude oil,
according to the Oslo-based newspaper. Authorities are working
on containing the leak around the vessel, which ran aground late
yesterday, the newspaper said.     Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
